OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScot Brian McBride         
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnominated as next CBI      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpresident                  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Scot who grew up in a council house  
OL,6, in Glasgow has been nominated to take  
OL,7, over as president of the leading UK    
OL,8, business organisation, the CBI.        
OL,10,FBrian McBride, one of eight children,  
OL,11,Fstarted his business life selling      
OL,12,Fphotocopiers for Xerox in the 1970s.   
OL,14,FHe then joined IBM before being hired  
OL,15,Fby Michael Dell to run Dell's          
OL,16,Foperations in UK and Northern Europe.  
OL,18,FHe built his career in digital and     
OL,19,Ftech, first as boss of T-Mobile, where 
OL,20,Fhe launched 3G in the UK.              
